Dick 10 years ago invented a much cheaper procedure: based on the customer identification code you can easily get information from the pharmacy on which medicine he bought in the last year and half and from this the evidence program of which diseases he suffers and under what health conditions he is in.
For example, if you regularly purchase large amounts of cholesterol reducers, this means that the fat level in the blood is in practice unguarantably high and is classified in the highest risk category.
